---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="New York Vaping Laws | Legal Edge Insights">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#0077b6] mb-8">New York State Vaping Laws</h1>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview of Vaping Regulations in New York</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">New York State has some of the strictest vaping regulations in the United States. Here's what you need to know about the current laws and regulations.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Age Restrictions</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Must be 21 or older to purchase vaping products</li>
        <li>ID verification required for all purchases</li>
        <li>Penalties for selling to underage individuals</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Flavour Restrictions</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">As of May 2020, New York banned the sale of flavoured vaping products, except for tobacco flavour. This includes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>All fruit flavours</li>
        <li>Candy flavours</li>
        <li>Mint and menthol flavours</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Location Restrictions</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">Vaping is prohibited in many of the same places where smoking is banned:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Workplaces</li>
        <li>Bars and restaurants</li>
        <li>Public transportation</li>
        <li>Parks and beaches</li>
        <li>Within 100 feet of school entrances</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Online Sales</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">New York has specific regulations regarding online and mail-order sales of vaping products:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Online retailers must be licensed</li>
        <li>Age verification required for delivery</li>
        <li>Signature required upon delivery</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Penalties for Violations</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">Violations of New York's vaping laws can result in:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Fines ranging from $50 to $2,000</li>
        <li>License suspension or revocation for retailers</li>
        <li>Potential criminal charges for serious violations</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Legal Disclaimer</h4>
        <p class="text-sm">This information is provided for general educational purposes only and should not be considered legal advice. Laws and regulations may change. Consult with a qualified legal professional for specific guidance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
